CMD(PID=22408): /bin/sh -c failcom='exit 1'; \
for f in x $MAKEFLAGS; do \
  case $f in \
    *=* | --[!k]*);; \
    *k*) failcom='fail=yes';; \
  esac; \
done; \
dot_seen=no; \
target=`echo all-recursive | sed s/-recursive//`; \
list='docroot'; for subdir in $list; do \
  echo "Making $target in $subdir"; \
  if test "$subdir" = "."; then \
    dot_seen=yes; \
    local_target="$target-am"; \
  else \
    local_target="$target"; \
  fi; \
  (CDPATH="${ZSH_VERSION+.}:" && cd $subdir && /afs/cs.wisc.edu/u/w/e/wenbin/private/lighttpd-1.5.0/../vizmake/make/make  $local_target) \
  || eval $failcom; \
done; \
if test "$dot_seen" = "no"; then \
  /afs/cs.wisc.edu/u/w/e/wenbin/private/lighttpd-1.5.0/../vizmake/make/make  "$target-am" || exit 1; \
fi; test -z "$fail"
